### ===== DOCUMENTS & LIBREDESK INTEGRATION =====

### Create Driver Documents (triggers LibreDesk ticket creation)
POST {{base_url}}/driver/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9XrVIHqpzRWOqYT3Sv-7_hqlx_nr665zQvm-MojRdsk

{
  "aadharNumber": "123456789012",
  "panNumber": "ABCDE1234F",
  "licenseNumber": "DL12345678901234",
  "licenseUrl": "https://example.com/license.jpg",
  "fcUrl": "https://example.com/fc.jpg",
  "insuranceUrl": "https://example.com/insurance.jpg",
  "rcBookUrl": "https://example.com/rcbook.jpg",
  "suggestedLicenseExpiry": "2025-12-31",
  "suggestedFcExpiry": "2025-06-30",
  "suggestedInsuranceExpiry": "2025-03-31",
  "suggestedRcBookExpiry": "2025-09-30"
}

### Get Driver Documents
GET {{base_url}}/driver/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9XrVIHqpzRWOqYT3Sv-7_hqlx_nr665zQvm-MojRdsk

### Update Driver Documents (triggers LibreDesk ticket creation for re-verification)
PUT {{base_url}}/driver/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9XrVIHqpzRWOqYT3Sv-7_hqlx_nr665zQvm-MojRdsk

{
  "licenseUrl": "https://example.com/update-license.jpg",
  "suggestedLicenseExpiry": "2027-12-31"
}

### Get Upload URL for Document
POST {{base_url}}/driver/documents/upload-url
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9XrVIHqpzRWOqYT3Sv-7_hqlx_nr665zQvm-MojRdsk

{
  "filePath": "driver-documents/license.jpg",
  "type": "image/jpeg"
}

### Validate Aadhaar Number (check for duplicates)
POST {{base_url}}/driver/documents/validate-aadhar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9XrVIHqpzRWOqYT3Sv-7_hqlx_nr665zQvm-MojRdsk

{
  "aadharNumber": "987654321098"
}

### Validate PAN Number (check for duplicates)
POST {{base_url}}/driver/documents/validate-pan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..9XrVIHqpzRWOqYT3Sv-7_hqlx_nr665zQvm-MojRdsk

{
